# Account Deletion – Parish Directory App

The Parish Directory App is developed by **Jojo Thomas** for **Thekkan Parumala St. Gregorios Orthodox Valiya Pally** members.  
This page explains how users can request deletion of their account and associated data.

---

## How to Request Account Deletion
To delete your account and associated data:
1. Send an email to the App administration team [aileronlogic@gmail.com] with the subject line: *Account Deletion Request – Parish Directory App*.
2. Include your registered email address used in the app.
3. The church administration will verify your identity and confirm the deletion request.
4. Once verified, your account and associated data will be permanently deleted.

---

## Data Deleted
When your account is deleted, the following data will be removed:
- Member profile (name, contact information, ward assignment, roll number)
- Family relationships linked to your profile
- Profile photo (if provided)
- Birthday information

---

## Data Retained
- Aggregated, non‑identifiable statistics may be retained for internal reporting.
- Records required for parish administration may be retained for compliance purposes.

---

## Retention Period
- Account and associated data are deleted within **30 days** of a verified request.
- If you uninstall the app without requesting deletion, your data remains until you submit a deletion request.

---

## Partial Data Deletion (Optional)
If you wish to request deletion of **specific data only** (e.g., profile photo or birthday), without deleting your account:
- Contact the App administration team [aileronlogic@gmail.com].
- Specify the data you want removed.
- Such requests will be processed within **30 days**.

---

## Contact
For account deletion or data removal requests, please contact:

**Thekkan Parumala St. Gregorios Orthodox Valiya Pally**  
Email: aileronlogic@gmail.com [App Admin Team]

